com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.util

Class MockObjects

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.util.MockObjects

  • public class MockObjects
extends java.lang.Object

    Helper Class.
    Takes an url, creates a WebRequest, creates and uses a WebClient to load the WebResponse. Can parse the content of the WebResponse into a LightWeightPage, as well as a HtmlPage
    This can be done at one go (via load()), or stepwise.

    Used for Debugging and Testing.
    Author:
    matthias mitterreiter
